subject: Tour of California (Bicycle Race)
Bicycles and Bicycling
lead_paragraph: Levi Leipheimer finished 36 seconds ahead of David Zabriskie of Garmin-Slipstream, and 45 seconds in front of Michael Rogers of Columbia-Highroad.
